= raw "#{ link_to @user.name, user_url(@user.username) } assign #{@teams.count} teams to #{ link_to @group.name, group_url(@group.path) } group:"
%br
%table
  %caption Assigned teams
  %tr
    %th Name
  - @teams.each do |t|
    %tr
      %td
        = link_to team_url(t.path) do
          = "#{ t.name } (#{ t.path })"
%br
%br
NOTE: All teams members has access to groups teams with access, configured in each team.
